---

---

<section id="infos" class="border-b border-neutral-900 bg-black">
  <div
    class="container-narrow py-14 sm:py-20 grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.4fr)_minmax(0,1fr)]"
  >
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-neutral-500">
        Studio & réservation
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
        Informations pratiques.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-300">
        Le studio clm.ink se situe au cœur de Chambéry. Tout se fait uniquement
        sur rendez-vous, pour des projets préparés ensemble en amont à partir de
        vos envies, références et contraintes.
      </p>
      <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-sm">
        <div class="space-y-1 sm:col-span-2">
          <dt class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-500">
            Localisation
          </dt>
          <dd class="text-neutral-100">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
              <a
                href="https://www.google.com/maps?q=4+Rue+Claude+Martin,+73000+Chamb%C3%A9ry"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="text-base font-semibold leading-relaxed hover:text-neutral-50 transition-colors"
              >
                4 rue Claude Martin<br />
                73000 Chambéry, France
                <div class="mt-1 text-xs font-normal text-neutral-400">
                  sur rendez-vous uniquement<br />
                  Du mardi au samedi.
                </div>
              </a>
              <div
                class="w-28 h-28 sm:w-32 sm:h-32 rounded-xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-950/60 overflow-hidden shrink-0"
              >
                <img
                  src="/map.png"
                  alt="Plan d'accès au studio clm.ink — 4 rue Claude Martin, Chambéry"
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="h-full w-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </dd>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1 sm:col-span-2">
          <dt class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-500">
            Collectif
          </dt>
          <dd class="text-neutral-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-neutral-700 bg-neutral-950/80 overflow-hidden shrink-0">
                <img
                  src="/purple_line.jpg"
                  alt="Purple Line tattoo club"
                  loading="lazy"
                  class="h-full w-full object-cover"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                clm.ink partage son studio au sein du collectif
                <a
                  href="https://www.instagram.com/purpleline.tattoo/"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noreferrer"
                  class="whitespace-nowrap underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-500 hover:decoration-neutral-200"
                >
                  Purple Line tattoo club
                </a>
                , qui réunit six tatoueurs :
                <span class="block text-xs text-neutral-400 mt-1 space-x-1">
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/suzon_tattoo/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-300"
              >
                @suzon_tattoo
              </a>
              <span>·</span>
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/m.caligari/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-300"
              >
                @m.caligari
              </a>
              <span>·</span>
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/bonjour.crapule/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-300"
              >
                @bonjour.crapule
              </a>
              <span>·</span>
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/cotenoir.ink/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-300"
              >
                @cotenoir.ink
              </a>
              <span>·</span>
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/clm.ink/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-300"
              >
                @clm.ink
              </a>
              <span>·</span>
              <a
                href="https://www.instagram.com/primo_kao.tattoo/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-600 hover:decoration-neutral-300"
              >
                @primo_kao.tattoo
              </a>
            </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-500">
        Pour toute question sur l&apos;hygiène, la cicatrisation ou les
        conditions de réservation, consultez les pages
        <a
          href="/studio-hygiene"
          class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-500 hover:decoration-neutral-200"
          >« Studio &amp; hygiène »</a
        >
        et
        <a
          href="/faq-tatouage"
          class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-neutral-500 hover:decoration-neutral-200"
          >« FAQ tatouage »</a
        >.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      id="contact"
      class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-950/70 p-6"
    >
      <h3
        class="text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-neutral-200"
      >
        Prendre contact
      </h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400">
        Les réservations se font principalement via Instagram ou par e-mail.
        Donnez un maximum de détails sur votre projet (zone, style, taille
        approximative, budget, photos de référence si besoin).
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
        <a
          href="https://www.instagram.com/clm.ink/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-full border border-neutral-700 px-4 py-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-100 hover:border-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-100 hover:text-black transition-colors"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-4 w-4">
              <rect
                x="3"
                y="3"
                width="18"
                height="18"
                rx="5"
                class="fill-none stroke-current"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect>
              <circle
                cx="12"
                cy="12"
                r="4"
                class="fill-none stroke-current"
                stroke-width="1.4"></circle>
              <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" class="fill-current"></circle>
            </svg>
            <span>DM Instagram</span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-400">@clm.ink</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:hello@clm.ink?subject=Projet%20tatouage%20-%20clm.ink"
          class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-full border border-neutral-800 px-4 py-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-neutral-200 hover:border-neutral-100 hover:text-neutral-50 transition-colors"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="h-4 w-4">
              <rect
                x="3"
                y="5"
                width="18"
                height="14"
                rx="2"
                class="fill-none stroke-current"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect>
              <path
                d="m5 7 7 5 7-5"
                class="fill-none stroke-current"
                stroke-width="1.4"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Email</span>
          </span>
          <span class="text-[10px] text-neutral-500">hello@clm.ink</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-[11px] text-neutral-500">
        Un acompte pourra être demandé pour bloquer une date. Les mineurs
        doivent être accompagnés d&apos;un représentant légal, avec pièces
        d&apos;identité.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
